This is the Abu Abu Slider.

102
00:07:00,820 --> 00:07:03,460
Our company's No. 1 product!

103
00:07:03,460 --> 00:07:05,110
A new model has been
released! Give this a try!

104
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:08,800
