small sea breeze to get damaged.

146
00:08:55,210 --> 00:08:57,640
Then, please leave it to me.

147
00:08:58,070 --> 00:09:01,140
Transponder Snail Mail-Order
presents with confidence

148
00:09:01,340 --> 00:09:04,010
