175
00:10:11,300 --> 00:10:14,580
Okay, then... If you insist that much...

176
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:17,100
A ream of 1,000 A-Thousand-Year Papers

177
00:10:17,590 --> 00:10:19,870
normally costs 60 million Berries,

178
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:22,850
but how about a special price of 48 million?

179
00:10:23,090 --> 00:10:25,550
48 million Berries...!

180
00:10:25,550 --> 00:10:28,230
Does that mean that it costs
48,000 Berries a sheet?!

181
00:10:28,460 --> 00:10:30,920
Can't you drop the price a little more?

182
00:10:32,180 --> 00:10:33,610
Well then, I'll make it a lot cheaper...

183
00:10:33,610 --> 00:10:35,430
How about 47.5 million Berries?

184
00:10:35,430 --> 00:10:36,670
2 million Berries!

185
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:38,240
4.8 million Berries!

186
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,250
This sounds fishy...

187
00:10:39,250 --> 00:10:40,200
Can't you go cheaper?

188
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,470
We'll buy it!

189
00:10:42,210 --> 00:10:43,440
Sanji-kun...

190
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,150
You have the money?

191
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:45,910
Nope!

192
00:10:49,490 --> 00:10:52,840
But if we hand him over to the Navy,
we'll have that and change.

193
00:10:53,060 --> 00:10:55,590
What?!

194
00:10:56,260 --> 00:10:59,830
Sorry, Luffy. This is for Nami-san.

195
00:10:59,830 --> 00:11:01,050
Wait a sec!

196
00:11:01,530 --> 00:11:02,680
Luffy...?

197
00:11:03,140 --> 00:11:04,070
Ahh!

198
00:11:04,070 --> 00:11:08,270
Luffy... You mean... that Monkey D. Luffy?

199
00:11:08,610 --> 00:11:10,530
Yeah, that's me.

200
00:11:10,900 --> 00:11:12,980
Sanji! Whatever, just untie me.

201
00:11:13,290 --> 00:11:14,180
No, I can't.

202
00:11:14,180 --> 00:11:17,910
Th-Th-That odious pirate with
a 100 million-Berry bounty...

203
00:11:17,910 --> 00:11:19,560
That Monkey D. Luffy...?

204
00:11:20,020 --> 00:11:23,380
Come to think of it... that's a pirate flag!

205
00:11:24,970 --> 00:11:28,500
I can't believe I missed
such important details!

206
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:29,890
I said untie me!

207
00:11:29,890 --> 00:11:30,890
No!

208
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:32,000
Uhm...!

209
00:11:32,430 --> 00:11:35,500
I just remembered that I have
an important appointment.

210
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:36,470
Goodbye!

211
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,290
Thanks for everything!

212
00:11:39,290 --> 00:11:40,930
Hey, you forgot something...!

213
00:11:46,070 --> 00:11:47,220
What's with him?

214
00:11:47,660 --> 00:11:49,910
Maybe he was scared of you...

215
00:11:50,220 --> 00:11:53,170
Wanted man, Monkey D. Luffy.

216
00:11:55,050 --> 00:11:56,740
Really...?

217
00:12:00,610 --> 00:12:04,760
Listen. I'm going to work now,
so don't interrupt me, okay?

218
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:07,030
What do you mean "work"?

219
